title: Various Professors and Resources on Neuro-Linguistic Programming (NLP) and Hypnosis
first_phrase: This text provides a list of experts and professionals in the fields of cinema, PNL, hypnosis, mentalism, acupuncture, and more, including their websites and contact information. The last 200 tokens list various websites associated with the school of Neurolinguistic Programming, including resources for free scanned ebooks, personal pages, and research in Nepal. These include the official website, an Italian site, an English site, and more.
